{"word":"H7663 - שָׂבַר - sâbar - saw-bar' - Hope","slug":"H7663","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂבַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sâbar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-bar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hope"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05D1;&#x05E8; - s&#x0301;a&#x0302;bar  sha&#x0302;bar</b> - <i>saw-bar', shaw-bar'</i><p/>The second form being used erroneously in <a href='B:160 2:13'>Neh 2:13</a>, <a href='B:160 2:15'>Neh 2:15</a>; a primitive root; to <i>scrutinize</i>; by implication (of <i>watching</i>) to <i>expect</i> (with hope and patience): - hope, tarry, view, wait."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7664\">H7664</a>"}]}